    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi Experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I am trying to explore one of the requirement, please find the details steps followed below&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;1) Created the CAP project - capanalysis&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_3-1711453759603.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86558iB167B3BF114D647E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_3-1711453759603.png" alt="oghadashi_3-1711453759603.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;2) Created the &lt;SPAN&gt;SAP HANA Schemas &amp;amp; HDI Containers instance with the HDI-shared plan and binded with the CAP project &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_5-1711453810548.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86562iF36A80854B7E32F8/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_5-1711453810548.png" alt="oghadashi_5-1711453810548.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;3) through Database explorer created the table DEMOTEST using sql statement instead of the hdbtable (reason : bcoz we need to replicate the table from another system).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_2-1711453723053.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86556iD90E757FF44E6393/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_2-1711453723053.png" alt="oghadashi_2-1711453723053.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;4) Made changes in the data modeling file accordingly and annotated it with the @cds.persistence.exists and service file.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_0-1711453641746.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86550i8729B48F08DD4703/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_0-1711453641746.png" alt="oghadashi_0-1711453641746.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_1-1711453672606.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86552i1E827BABD90B5C16/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_1-1711453672606.png" alt="oghadashi_1-1711453672606.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;5) executed the cds build command&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_6-1711453855779.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86564i2CD0F2CF43C07884/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_6-1711453855779.png" alt="oghadashi_6-1711453855779.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;6) While cds deploy i was facing the error "&lt;SPAN&gt;The file requires "db://DEMOTEST" which is not provided by any file"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;7) Going further through the reference, &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/hana-express-2-0-sps-01-the-file-requires-quot-db-sbook-quot-which-is-not/qaq-p/428781," target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/hana-express-2-0-sps-01-the-file-requires-quot-db-sbook-quot-which-is-not/qaq-p/428781.&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I added the hdbsynonym fil:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_7-1711454316109.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86569i797A7B37AE2C4AFA/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_7-1711454316109.png" alt="oghadashi_7-1711454316109.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":smiling_face_with_sunglasses:"&gt;😎&lt;/span&gt;again executed the cds build and cds deploy but facing the cyclic dependency issue&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="oghadashi_8-1711454407808.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/86572iB96412DDB887700B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="oghadashi_8-1711454407808.png" alt="oghadashi_8-1711454407808.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;It will be really great help you could guide me with the below issue ?&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Regards,&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Omkar&lt;/P&gt;</content>
