per lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="thejk_2-1711625968389.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/88020i1872CDB0DD017CFD/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="thejk_2-1711625968389.png" alt="thejk_2-1711625968389.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;I also tried these parameters, no success:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="thejk_3-1711626058640.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/88021iB767FD063233BE31/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="thejk_3-1711626058640.png" alt="thejk_3-1711626058640.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;My User has these Roles:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="thejk_5-1711626891915.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/88027iE402817E3AFE79A5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="thejk_5-1711626891915.png" alt="thejk_5-1711626891915.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;P&gt;Any hint is highly appreciated...&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Regards,&lt;BR /&gt;Jürgen&lt;/P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
